WindowsWear成立于2012年，是一家实时橱窗展示的时尚科技公司，总部位于纽约<ref>Yu, Samantha. [http://www.refinery29.com/windowswear "Better Than the Yule Log? The World's Holiday Windows At You Fingertips"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.refinery29.com/windowswear |date=20150809084834 }}, "[[Refinery29|Refinery29]]", 10 December 2012. Retrieved 4 June 2013.</ref>。WindowsWear擁有能夠追溯到1931年的時尚櫥窗及視覺陳列的檔案收藏，如此的收藏提供零售商、設計師、品牌，以及創意專業人士許多照片來進行多年以來的競爭力研究、靈感來源與流行趨勢的分析<ref>Young, Vicki. [http://wwd.com/retail-news/retail-features/lord-taylor-christmas-windows-a-look-over-the-years-10298592/] {{Wayback|url=http://wwd.com/retail-news/retail-features/lord-taylor-christmas-windows-a-look-over-the-years-10298592/ |date=20160901162528 }}, "[[WWD|WWD]]", 23 December 2015. Retrieved 9 February 2016.</ref>。

==商业运作==
公司有三大运营模块： windowswear.com主营橱窗购物；windowswearpro为订购的时尚领域数据服务；以及位于纽约的windowswear时尚观光之旅。目前，windowswear已获得来自高盛，巴克莱，coach，易购以及野村证券的注资<ref>Talwar, Pia.[http://www.fashinvest.com/windowswear-receives-friends-family-financing-one-year-anniversary/ "WindowsWear Receives a Friends and Family Round of Financing During Their One-Year Anniversary"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fashinvest.com/windowswear-receives-friends-family-financing-one-year-anniversary/ |date=20140116080158 }}, "FashInvest", 27 November 2013. Retrieved 14 January 2013.</ref>。

